    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Animal作为基类。那属性的类型您有偏好吗？比如name用String，age用int？另外是否需要加上可见性修饰符？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "name",
        "age"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，name用String，age用int。可见性都用public，因为子类需要直接访问这些属性。另外Animal还需要一个行为方法，makeSound，表示发出声音。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "name",
        "age",
        "makeSound"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把Animal类画出来：包含public的name（String类型）、age（int类型），以及public方法makeSound()。",
      "elements_involved": [
