    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认区分清楚了：name和age是属性，makeSound是方法。命名风格上，Java惯例是用camelCase，所以makeSound更合适。我按这个来。",
      "elements_involved": [
